    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >没有严格的类别</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/a91602ba3be23381df449bc74cb71429.poster.avif?t=1753956459\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/a91602ba3be23381df449bc74cb71429.webm?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/a91602ba3be23381df449bc74cb71429.mp4?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你可以创建<strong>你自己的类型</strong>，没有任何东西被锁定，随意扮演挥舞双手剑的火法师或死灵弓箭手。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >大量的发迹和技能</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/7820c9c47664aaf8640f05bbd129cbae.poster.avif?t=1753956459\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/7820c9c47664aaf8640f05bbd129cbae.webm?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/7820c9c47664aaf8640f05bbd129cbae.mp4?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在法术、武器、能力和发迹方面，有大量的选项。你可以创造大量的建筑并不断寻找新的方法来粉碎你的敌人！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基于技能的老式动作 RPG 砍杀战斗。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/05cfbfbf3d4715ec818cc926e9ed8892.poster.avif?t=1753956459\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/05cfbfbf3d4715ec818cc926e9ed8892.webm?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/05cfbfbf3d4715ec818cc926e9ed8892.mp4?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>体能固然重要，但躲避敌人攻击并瞄准自己的目标也同样重要！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >充满任务的开放世界</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/d7931498d0542415c8b5be5f254056cd.avif?t=1753956459\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>探索权利欲之世界，穿梭于各个城市之间，寻找神奇的宝藏，帮助非玩家角色找到丢失的牙齿等等！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >单人做的</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/f153c4b3ed043306b0ed99b88f2e7069.poster.avif?t=1753956459\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/f153c4b3ed043306b0ed99b88f2e7069.webm?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/f153c4b3ed043306b0ed99b88f2e7069.mp4?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>一个人（我）的业余项目。 我已经在这上面花了好几年了。不涉及庞大的公司 :)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >有趣的相机模式</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/dfb6948ee7609ccf85138b6401cb0910.poster.avif?t=1753956459\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/dfb6948ee7609ccf85138b6401cb0910.webm?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/dfb6948ee7609ccf85138b6401cb0910.mp4?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在等距、俯视、第三人称视角和第一人称视角的相机模式之间选择游戏方式！ 使用有趣的相机滤镜，让游戏看起来独一无二。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >我很想听听你的反馈</h2>我还在制作这款游戏。 如果会有任何反馈意见，对进一步的开发工作很有帮助，我将不胜感激。 请关注我的 twitter 以获取不断更新，并通过电子邮件或 <strong>discord</strong> 分享你的想法！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >功能：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>按程序生成的地牢。      <br></li><li>基于技能的战斗。      <br></li><li>没有严格的类别。 <br></li><li>大量的发迹、物品、技能和建筑。      <br></li><li>开放的世界可供探索。      <br></li><li>可选择永久死亡。      <br></li><li>控制器支持。    <br></li><li>很棒的不和谐社区。</li></ul>",
